<lb/><p rend="right">Pearl Steamer </p>
<lb/><p rend="right">21<hi rend="sup">st</hi> April 
<lb/>1858</p>
<lb/><p><persName>Sir George Grey K.C.B.</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I have the honour 
<lb/>to forward two letters for 
<lb/>your Excellency and beg 
<lb/>leave to say that the 
<lb/>Pearl in which we 
<lb/>are sailing for the 
<lb/><placeName>Zambesi</placeName> will leave 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001310_0002"/><!--pb/@n='02'-->
<lb/><placeName>Table Bay</placeName> tomorrow 
<lb/>forenoon in order to 
<lb/>coal at <placeName>Simon's Bay</placeName>
<lb/>but I shall take the 
<lb/>liberty of calling on 
<lb/>your Excellency before 
<lb/>she departs<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
